@fields.neighbour: "Stop making so much noise!" 
@fields.guide_teen: "I hate you!"

It is so hard to tell teenagers what to do! What really helped me was to change how to ask my teen to do things. Now, I tell them what they should do instead of what they shouldn’t. Let me show you how it works!
